{"tid":190401,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"D小朋友日日開POST 屌呢到低質，俾哂解決方法又視而不見","createTime":"2017-04-07T05:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T05:47:11.000Z","uid":26115,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7281b1ae5d171689cbe71e6fa98c2202abac0103","tid":190401,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:56:16.000Z","msg":"留係波台笑下算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連尼住你賺埋呢半年廣告費啦，過多排又有人移民架喇"},{"pid":"e50ea9ee2b84bf3b3e57458d199f4f10ddd5e0f7","tid":190401,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T06:02:18.000Z","msg":"每次果D「低質」POST個發展都係樓豬話連登好低質，然後一班人認同同正評，但係冇人提解決方法，成班人圍埋打飛機，到有人提解決方法就冇人理，跟住波台手足就會入場，班人就會講:「寧要五毛不要波台。」個POST之後就會俾波台手足推爆。<br />\n<br />\n然後，過兩日又有一個「低質」POST。"},{"pid":"76fb5abb4d9b8e950d5db46a2457d975cb82d3ae","tid":190401,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T06:47:29.000Z","msg":"樓主係高質會員"},{"pid":"fa564367af3e2b6e34af8f0a4a8c485f637e1bb2","tid":190401,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T06:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb8e6dc05ee36dd92a50872fd756ae133e10dd2","tid":190401,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係高質會員</blockquote><br />\n反連旗幟鮮明"},{"pid":"458d645aa7cacc979bf815f69ff93fc05af45150","tid":190401,"uid":11579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:06:40.000Z","msg":"留名等睇樓主所講既「解決方法」"},{"pid":"4cf6d8abe2a4f511f2a029ad252708ce707142ee","tid":190401,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名等睇樓主所講既「解決方法」</blockquote><br />\n所有野都係波台嘅錯，拖累cc政事台，感情，成人台，創意娛樂台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c5d170cd8282514cfdc769e21e9b3f8a796950","tid":190401,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:14:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名等睇樓主所講既「解決方法」</blockquote><br />\n自己追post啦屌你老母，講十幾萬次都要做伸手黨<br />\n而家心水清D都知熱門有問題，屌撚左兩個星期ADMIN一個回應都冇(除左人手搬左我個PO上熱門)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/167459/page/38\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/167459/page/38</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/186348/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/186348/page/1</a><br />\n不過唔撚緊要，你班垃圾淨係識睇5P字，然後將所有問題推落去5P字到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ec9ddb1a145d08f7f1a552683ebfdf6400c224","tid":190401,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:15:53.000Z","msg":"ching ho ball"},{"pid":"624bf31d3cb8cb7ad5fc239e969b32dc252d5437","tid":190401,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"留名睇波台小學雞入黎嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decd52124eb9a289482600efa64cd6b0a27604bc","tid":190401,"uid":22580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇波台小學雞入黎嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主咪波台小學雞😂"},{"pid":"8c83ed20211f4f15e3635910991997badac1f149","tid":190401,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T08:24:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"683dc28395a69960d29e6da36bcf6be5d6457fde","tid":190401,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T08:27:31.000Z","msg":"洗撚理佢地咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1.同連狗無親，個壇低質關我撚事<br />\n2.d人低質我又唔會痛<br />\n3.波台手足既質素唔會因爲個壇而下降<br />\n4.golden apps整返好用我就返去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\